    <item>
      <title>高油价意味着 2025 年欧洲消费者开局艰难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/high-gas-prices-spell-tough-start-to-2025-for-european-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年欧洲天然气价格上涨了约 45%，这给努力从几十年来最严重的生活成本危机中恢复的家庭和工业增加了负担。随着俄罗斯天然气供应将于 1 月 1 日停止，未来可能还会有更多天然气价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/high-gas-prices-spell-tough-start-to-2025-for-european-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 13:19:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行的凯特纳认为许多行业将支持市场扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-30/hsbc-plenty-of-sectors-to-support-market-broadening-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行首席多元资产策略师 Max Kettner 解释了为什么他认为进入 2025 年，市场“仍将拥有相当大的发展势头”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-30/hsbc-plenty-of-sectors-to-support-market-broadening-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 13:17:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普回归前，加拿大人对经济越来越悲观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/canadians-are-growing-pessimistic-about-economy-ahead-of-trump-s-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的关税威胁给美国最大的贸易伙伴之一带来了不确定性，加拿大人对经济走向的乐观程度比一年多前有所下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/canadians-are-growing-pessimistic-about-economy-ahead-of-trump-s-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡洛斯·斯利姆在 2024 年投资 10 亿美元，增强石油投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/carlos-slim-invested-1-billion-in-2024-to-supercharge-oil-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲首富卡洛斯·斯利姆今年投入 10 亿美元扩大其原油生产和炼制业务，因为他认为对化石燃料的需求不会很快消失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/carlos-slim-invested-1-billion-in-2024-to-supercharge-oil-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街年底涨势消退，欧洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/european-stocks-drop-as-traders-watch-inflation-ecb-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市在 2024 年倒数第二个交易日下跌，这是该地区今年的小幅上涨，与华尔街的看涨反弹形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/european-stocks-drop-as-traders-watch-inflation-ecb-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:22:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙通胀加速，支持欧洲央行逐步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-backing-gradual-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙 12 月份通胀率升幅超出预期，受基数效应影响，通胀率连续第二个月维持在 2% 以上，这为逐步降息提供了依据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-backing-gradual-ecb-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者关注 2025 年风险，油价在清淡交投中小幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员关注 2025 年的风险（从充足的供应到即将上任的特朗普政府的不可预测性），油价小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Dec 2024 23:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
